metadata.name: Veni
metadata.description:
Whatever betrayal sundered these angels from the celestial gardens where they lived and played, we may never know. Yet we know they are here, and what they are, as one cannot help but be overcome by the mystifyingly pure and ethereal light they radiate.

These beautiful souls have been captured in muted settings and lit so softly, that their innate form and being shines beyond everything else.
